Package no longer supported - will not receive further updates.

Home Assistant has deprecated the "Core" installation method (running inside a
Python virtual environment), which is exactly how this Synology package runs.
Support ended with release 2025.12: the Core method no longer receives updates,
including security updates. Only Home Assistant OS and Home Assistant Container
remain supported.

Ref: https://www.home-assistant.io/blog/2025/05/22/deprecating-core-and-supervised-installation-methods-and-32-bit-systems/
